query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angular5',
'azure-cosmosdb',
'data-science',
'firebase-storage',
'installation',
'jasper-reports',
'jinja2',
'nsarray',
'repository',
'row',
'rubygems',
'sparql',
'url-redirection',
'webserver');
